Description:
--------------

	This simple script installs packages that are listed in the packages.txt
	file. It also updates and upgrades your applications.

How to run: 
--------------
	Put whatever package you want to install in packages.txt file LINE BY LINE. 
 	Note: make sure you reserve a last void line for the script to run
 	properly.

 	Open terminal in the same directory and run:

 		sudo ./essenpk.sh
